text: Hesham Mustafa (born 1 July 1952) is a former Iraqi football forward who played for Iraq in the 1976 AFC Asian Cup. Hesham played for the national team between 1975 and 1976. ==References== Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Iraq international footballers Category:1976 AFC Asian Cup players Category:Living people Category:Association football forwards Category:1952 births
